<paragraph blockId="36.[264,1325,608,1851]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[312,376,1415,1439]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
<typeStatus box="[312,376,1415,1439]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Types</typeStatus>
</emphasis>
: The 
<typeStatus box="[444,540,1415,1438]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">syntypes</typeStatus>
, at least two, in 
<collectionCode LSID="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34991" box="[722,803,1415,1438]" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34991" name="Hungarian Natural History Museum (Termeszettudomanyi Muzeum)" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">HNHM</collectionCode>
