<number box="[984,1040,1415,1438]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" value="1956.0">1956</number>
. Bezzi (
<number box="[1129,1184,1415,1438]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" value="1921.0">1921</number>
a) listed four 
<typeStatus box="[360,453,1444,1467]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">syntypes</typeStatus>
in 
<collectionCode box="[496,572,1444,1467]" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/94p5-pepz" name="Iziko Museums of Cape Town" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">SAMC</collectionCode>
